{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.320", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.080", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.600", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung will mit dem vorliegenden Antrag den Einsatz von fast 1\u00a0000 deutschen Soldaten in Afghanistan verl\u00e4ngern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.960", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um das gleich zu Beginn mit aller Deutlichkeit zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.560", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die AfD-Fraktion lehnt diesen Antrag als absolut unvern\u00fcnftig und absolut unverantwortlich ab."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.400", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drei Gr\u00fcnde will ich Ihnen nennen:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.760", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.680", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Niemand hier im Haus kann die Lage in Afghanistan wirklich kennen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.840", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor drei Jahren legte die Bundesregierung einen letzten Fortschrittsbericht vor. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.240", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Seitdem hat es keinen einzigen seri\u00f6sen Lagebericht mehr gegeben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.200", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "keine ehrliche Bilanzierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.560", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "keine unabh\u00e4ngige Evaluation. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.280", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer hier und heute im Sinne der Bundesregierung entscheidet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der entscheidet schlichtweg blind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.440", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.480", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr die Mission in Afghanistan gibt es kein explizites Mandat der Vereinten Nationen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.440", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer aber\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.480", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir als AfD\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.960", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die zentrale Rolle der Vereinten Nationen f\u00fcr internationale Sicherheit und Weltfrieden anerkennt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.920", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der kann ein fehlendes UN-Mandat nicht einfach ignorieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.680", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau das aber tut die Bundesregierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.560", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und sie tut es seit drei Jahren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.000", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.320", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die NATO-Mission in Afghanistan kann man als klassisches Nation-Building verstehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.560", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und laut Antrag der Bundesregierung ist es ausdr\u00fccklich kein Kampfeinsatz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.880", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es war gerade im August\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.520", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor wenigen Monaten\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.400", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da stellte sich der US-Pr\u00e4sident Donald Trump vor die Kameras dieser Welt und erkl\u00e4rte seine neue Afghanistan-Strategie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.800", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dort sagte er: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.360", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir betreiben kein Nation-Building. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.560", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir t\u00f6ten Terroristen.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.720", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist aus meiner Sicht kein lapidares Abweichen von unserer Strategie in Afghanistan. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.800", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist exakt das Gegenteil unserer Strategie in Afghanistan."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.960", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.560", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "seit 16\u00a0Jahren ist die NATO unter deutscher Beteiligung am Hindukusch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.640", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir alle kennen die katastrophale Bilanz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.560", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kaum ein Land auf dieser Welt ist korrupter\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.600", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "glauben Sie mir; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.320", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn ich habe es als Soldat im Einsatz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.120", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der dort sechs Monate verbracht hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.240", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "selbst erlebt\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.120", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kaum ein Land ist mehr vom Terror betroffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.600", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und bei der Opiumproduktion liegt Afghanistan weltweit auf Platz eins. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.360", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "56\u00a0deutsche Soldaten mussten den Einsatz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.640", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der diese katastrophale Bilanz aufweist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.800", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit ihrem Leben bezahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.280", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und doch will die Bundesregierung allen Misserfolgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.920", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "R\u00fcckschl\u00e4gen und Opfern zum Trotz erneut deutsche Soldaten nach Afghanistan entsenden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.560", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "obwohl kein UN-Mandat vorliegt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.760", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "obwohl niemand hier wei\u00df, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.920", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie die Lage in Afghanistan wirklich aussieht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.520", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und obwohl von einer abgestimmten NATO-Strategie sicherlich nicht mehr die Rede sein kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.600", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht mit uns, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.760", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.040", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht mit der AfD! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.880", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir lehnen diesen Antrag der Bundesregierung ab."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.200", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke sch\u00f6n."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.080", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chster Redner in der Debatte: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.960", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alexander Graf Lambsdorff f\u00fcr die FDP-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}